casebody.data:
Rene M. SPENCER, n/k/a Rene M. Sturdavant, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
William S. SPENCER, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158254
COA: 342513 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the motion for reconsideration of this Court's December 4, 2018 order is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that reconsideration of our previous order is warranted. MCR 7.311(G).
